reorder. The only exceptions are damaged products, lost shipments, or situations where the law requires a refund or replacement. We'll always take care of you if something goes wrong with delivery.<\/p>"}},"faq_7U98id":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"Can I change my shipping address?","answer":"<p>Yes, as long as your order hasn't been locked for fulfillment. Email help@doingwell.health with your order number and new address. Once the warehouse has started preparing your order, we may not be able to change it.<\/p>"}},"faq_N9RWHk":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"What is the Insider Club?","answer":"<p>The Insider Club is our founding group of customers from this secret preorder. You stay in the Insider Club as long as your doingwell subscription stays active. Members get early access to new flavors and products, special drops, giveaway entries, and insider-only updates before anyone else.<\/p>"}},"faq_JkPCB8":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"How does the subscription work?","answer":"<p>Your first box is $50 + $4.99 shipping. After that, you'll automatically be enrolled in a $55\/month subscription with free shipping unless you cancel before your next charge. As long as you stay subscribed, you keep your Insider Club membership.<\/p>"}},"faq_WEyaCX":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"What makes doingwell different?","answer":"<p>doingwell is built for people who actually train. High sodium to match heavy sweat, zero sugar, no stevia, no sugar alcohols, no artificial colors—just clean ingredients. Every batch is NSF Certified for Sport, the same standard required by pro leagues.<\/p>"}},"faq_RKYQXx":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"What flavors are available?","answer":"<p>The first drop includes two flavors: Coconut Lime and Raspberry. Both are naturally flavored with no artificial colors or dyes. Insider Club members will get first access to test new flavors before public release.<\/p>"}},"faq_jnUEbY":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"Will this product be available later?","answer":"<p>After this preorder, doingwell electrolytes will be sold at $55 on subscription with free shipping. The secret preorder is the only way into the Insider Club, and once it's over, we may not run this exact offer again. No guaranteed restock timing.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq_LeUr76","faq_TwMefk","faq_7U98id","faq_N9RWHk","faq_JkPCB8","faq_WEyaCX","faq_RKYQXx","faq_jnUEbY"],"name":"DW FAQ v2","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/kalyxi_favicon.png","enable_image_glow":true,"enable_image_border":true,"content_width":55,"eyebrow":"GOT QUESTIONS?","heading":"Frequently Asked Questions","heading_gradient":true,"subheading":"Everything you need to know about doingwell electrolytes.","show_numbers":true,"first_open":true,"button_text":"","button_url":"","button_icon":true,"button_style":"primary","button_radius":30,"button_bg_color":"#afc3f9","button_text_color":"#fafafa","button_border_color":"","button_gradient_1":"#afc3f9","button_gradient_2":"#00d4ff","bg_image_position_desktop":"center center","bg_image_position_mobile":"center center","bg_overlay_opacity":85,"background_color":"#f8f0e3","text_color":"#000000","heading_color":"#afc3f9","accent_color":"#5d0a01","border_color":"#afc3f9","glow_color_1":"#afc3f9","glow_color_2":"#afc3f9","enable_background_glow":true,"padding_desktop":100,"padding_mobile":50}}},"order":["dw_collection_1_wkbU9P","section","main","dw_faq_1_MJUMgx"]}